thread.title: Cassandra Price

author: Cassandra Price
title: Cassandra Price
text: We looked online, the first number we called although a local number was a call center to make appts and then we got a confirmation email on the email was the number of the place we called that number and asked if truck was available and if unit was available same day! it was! Great service even though call center was very deceptive the place itself is great!
